doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')

        title Geo-Fetch

        // Favicon
        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

        // Bootstrap icons
        link(href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.4.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css', rel='stylesheet')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/leaflet/1.7.1/leaflet.min.css')
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')
        
    body

        // Unavailable Popup
        #error-popup.popup.hidden
            p Data Unavailable !

        // Responsive navbar
        nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.bg-dark
            .container.px-5
                a.navbar-brand(href='index.html') Geo-Fetch
                button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarSupportedContent', aria-controls='navbarSupportedContent', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    span.navbar-toggler-icon
                #navbarSupportedContent.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ms-auto.mb-2.mb-lg-0
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='index.html') Home
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='https://kapilgrv.in', target='_blank') About
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='contact.html') Contact
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='services.html') Services

        // Header
        header.bg-dark.py-5
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.justify-content-center
                    .col-lg-6
                        .text-center.my-5
                            h1.display-5.fw-bolder.text-white.mb-2 IP to Geo-Location
                            p.lead.text-white-50.mb-4 Get location details of the IP based. Works on both IPV4 and IPV6. Read below for more details on how this works.
                            form(style="width: 100%;")
                                input(type="text", id="inputIp", placeholder="Please enter IPV4 or IPV6 here", style="width: 51%; text-align: center;")
                                br
                                br
                            .d-grid.gap-3.d-sm-flex.justify-content-sm-center
                                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.px-4.me-sm-3(onclick='fetchLocDetailsByIP()') Fetch Details
                                a.btn.btn-outline-light.btn-lg.px-4(href='#features') Learn More

        // Response section
        section#response-section.py-5.border-bottom(style="display: none;")
            .container.px-5.my-5
                .row.gx-5
                    .col-lg-12.mb-5.mb-lg-0
                        h2.h4.fw-bolder Location details
                        br
                        div#map

        // Features section
        section#features.py-5.border-bottom
            .container.px-5.my-5
                .row.gx-5
                    .col-lg-10.mb-5.mb-lg-0
                        .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-3
                            i.bi.bi-collection
                        h2.h4.fw-bolder IP Geolocation
                        p
                            | IP to location is the process of determining the geographic location of an Internet Protocol (IP) address. This information can be used for a variety of purposes, such as targeted advertising, content delivery, security, and fraud prevention.
                            br
                            br
                            | There are several ways to convert an IP address to a location, and the technique used here is using a geolocation database.
                            br
                            br
                            | There are several commercial and free geolocation databases available, such as MaxMind, IP2Location, and GeoLite. These databases contain mappings between IP addresses and their corresponding locations based on various factors, including IP routing and internet service provider (ISP) information.
                            br
                            br
                            strong It's important to note that IP-to-location conversions are not always accurate, as IP addresses can be assigned to ISPs that serve a wide geographic area or can be hidden behind a proxy or VPN, making it appear as if the user is in a different location.
                        a.text-decoration-none(href='api.html')
                            | Get API access for bulk operation / Automation
                            i.bi.bi-arrow-right

        // Contact section
        section.bg-light.py-5
            .container.px-5.my-5.px-5
                .text-center.mb-5
                    .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-3
                        i.bi.bi-envelope
                    h2.fw-bolder Get in touch
                    p.lead.mb-0 Would love to hear from you
                    a(href="mailto:kapilgrv@gmail.com") Send Email

        // Footer
        footer.py-5.bg-dark
            .container.px-5
                p.m-0.text-center.text-white Any feedback or collaboration initiatives are appreciated

        // Bootstrap core JS
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')

        // Core theme JS
        script(src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js")
        script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/leaflet/1.7.1/leaflet.min.js')
        script(src='js/scripts.js')

